➜疫情加剧俄罗斯人口危机，政府要开征“无子女税”？
http://www.sohu.com/a/425544526_114986	31305
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
